{"4375360": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "敗姬條款", "steam_appid": 4375360, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >關於此遊戲</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4375360/extras/4702f8208c97339f7db5dfdf16e1b9bd.avif?t=1774437181\" width=616 height=353 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在力量即是絕對真理的「索多瑪城」，一群狂妄的女性強者建立起不可撼動的獨裁統治。身為底層居民最後的變數，你將運用超凡的策略力量向權威發起挑戰。賭上一切進入《Terms of Surrender》的生死博弈，粉碎她們的高傲，讓這群不可一世的統治者在契約面前徹底臣服。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >擊敗強大BOSS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4375360/extras/ccc6221d7f160dc2fdec7394a00fc5b8.avif?t=1774437181\" width=464 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🎲 獨創五面骰策略系統</strong> 投擲五顆專屬骰子取戰鬥能量。且利用骰子結果觸發強大的特殊 BUFF(對子、胡蘆、full house等)，在關鍵回合扭轉戰局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>⚔️ 戰前自訂技能配置</strong> 面對強大的「姬」，策略從戰鬥前就已開始。根據敵人的屬性弱點，自由搭配你的技能組合，打造專屬的必勝流派。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>📜 策略性回合制對決</strong> 在純粹的回合制博弈中，精準計算能量與屬性剋制。透過智謀瓦解強敵的防線，贏得執行「投降條款」的權力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >有深度的戰鬥系統</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4375360/extras/142977292608f5c6c25aaa13fbc0db01.avif?t=1774437181\" width=577 height=325 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4375360/extras/0f55c0201f10e9ddf5f8e93b5b98abb8.avif?t=